<h2>Discussion:</h2>
<p>
<div class="post"><p><span class="name">Ayush Yash Shrestha</span> said: <div class="postcontent"><p>These maps are absolutely fantastic! The use of transforms to add more meaning to the same map is a real eye opener. The Electoral College cartogram in particular real hammers home the result.<br><br>The normal maps too are interesting. I wonder how convoluted the maps would look with multiple identifying criteria. e.g. male and single, male and married, female and single and female and married.</p></div>
